Interface NumberType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AObject, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, NamedElement, NonListType, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, PropertyType, Type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AadlInteger, AadlReal
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AadlIntegerImpl, AadlRealImpl, NumberTypeImpl

    public interface NumberType
extends NonListType
    A representation of the model object 'Number Type'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Owned Units Type
    • Units Type
    • Range
